---
import GitHubIcon from "../icons/GitHubIcon.astro";
---

<div class="flex flex-col bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-xl p-6 hover:bg-slate-700/80 hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-all group">
    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">AutoParts</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4 flex-1 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        Plataforma web de e-commerce para la venta de repuestos automotrices y visualización de información, detalle 
        y carrito de compras con su respectivo backend. <br>
        Proyecto Academico desarrolado con:
    </p>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/python/python-original.svg" alt="Python" title="Python" class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" />
        <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/django/django-plain.svg" alt="Django" title="Django" class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 bg-white/90 rounded-sm p-1" />
        <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/javascript/javascript-original.svg" alt="JavaScript" title="JavaScript" class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 rounded-sm" />
        <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/css3/css3-original.svg" alt="CSS3" title="CSS3" class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" />
    </div>
    <a href="https://github.com/yovngmamba8/autoparts" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 font-medium transition-colors mt-auto">
        <GitHubIcon class="w-5 h-5" />
        Ver Proyecto en GitHub
    </a>
</div>
